Package org.eclipse.emf.compare.ide.ui.internal.contentmergeviewer.tree.provider

Class TreeMergeViewerItemContentProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.compare.ide.ui.internal.contentmergeviewer.tree.provider.TreeMergeViewerItemContentProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMergeViewerItemContentProvider, IOptionalProvider
    public class TreeMergeViewerItemContentProvider
extends Object
implements IMergeViewerItemContentProvider
    ContentProvider for IMergeViewerItems which uses their 'left', 'right' and 'ancestor' sides in combination with the given AdapterFactory to create the children and parent IMergeViewerItems.
